                <h2>üè• Health Risks</h2>
                <p>Detailed medical information about food poisoning</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="health-section">
                <!-- Bacterial Infections -->
                <div class="bacterial-infections">
                    <h3>ü¶† Bacterial Infections</h3>
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #c62828;">Salmonella</h4>
                        <p><strong>Source:</strong> Raw eggs, poultry, meat, dairy products</p>
                        <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> Severe diarrhea, fever (up to 104¬∞F), stomach cramps</p>
                        <p><strong>Timeline:</strong> 6 hours to 6 days after eating contaminated food</p>
                        <p><strong>Complications:</strong> Dehydration, reactive arthritis, bloodstream infections</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #e65100;">E. coli</h4>
                        <p><strong>Source:</strong> Undercooked ground beef, raw vegetables, unpasteurized juice</p>
                        <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> Severe stomach cramps, bloody diarrhea, vomiting</p>
                        <p><strong>Complications:</strong> Hemolytic uremic syndrome (HUS) - kidney failure</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #2e7d32;">Listeria</h4>
                        <p><strong>Source:</strong> Deli meats, soft cheeses, unpasteurized milk</p>
                        <p><strong>Special Risk:</strong> 20x more likely to affect pregnant women</p>
                        <p><strong>Complications:</strong> Miscarriage, stillbirth, premature birth</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Mold Toxins -->
                <div class="mold-toxins">
                    <h3>üçÑ Mold Toxins</h3>
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #6a1b9a;">Aflatoxins</h4>
                        <p><strong>Found in:</strong> Peanuts, corn, tree nuts, grains stored in warm, humid conditions</p>
                        <p><strong>Health Effects:</strong> Most potent natural liver carcinogen known</p>
                        <p><strong>Long-term Risk:</strong> Liver cancer, immune suppression</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #0277bd;">Ochratoxin A</h4>
                        <p><strong>Found in:</strong> Stored grains, coffee beans, dried fruits</p>
                        <p><strong>Health Effects:</strong> Kidney damage, immune system suppression</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Botulism Warning -->
                <div class="botulism-warning">
                    <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è BOTULISM - The Most Deadly</h3>
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #b71c1c;">Clostridium botulinum</h4>
                        <p><strong>Source:</strong> Improperly canned foods, garlic in oil, baked potatoes in foil</p>
                        <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> Blurred vision, drooping eyelids, difficulty breathing</p>
                        <p><strong>Mortality Rate:</strong> 5-10% even with treatment</p>
                        <p><strong>Medical Emergency:</strong> Requires immediate hospitalization</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Emergency Response -->
                <div class="emergency-response">
                    <h4>üö® FOOD POISONING EMERGENCY - WHEN TO CALL 911</h4>
                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">
                        <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;">
                            <h5 style="color: #c62828;">üö® CALL IMMEDIATELY:</h5>
                            <ul style="color: #d32f2f;">
                                <li>Difficulty breathing or swallowing</li>
                                <li>Double vision or blurred vision</li>
                                <li>Severe dehydration (no urination for 8+ hours)</li>
                                <li>Blood in vomit or stool</li>
                                <li>Signs of botulism (drooping eyelids)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;">
