                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 10px 0;">
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>48 million Americans</strong> get food poisoning annually</li>
                            <li><strong>128,000 hospitalizations</strong> each year</li>
